H0.text: Water is the solvent in an aqueous solution.

H1.text: Oil is the solvent in an aqueous solution.

H2.text: Any liquid is the solvent in an aqueous solution.

H3.text: Saltwater is the solvent in an aqueous solution.

A4.text: An aqueous solution is a solution in which the solvent is water.

A5.text: A non-aqueous solution is a solution in which the solvent is a liquid, but is not water.
